 <label class="label">Table 1</label>
 <caption class="caption">
  <p class="p">Examples of climate extremes leading to migration and conflict since 2000. Despite the increasing body of literature on the theory and potential for climate related migration to result in conflict, there are surprisingly few case studies on recent climate extremes that lead to migration and conflict (see Reuveny, 2007 for a meta-analysis of historical examples) [
   <xref rid="B1-ijerph-13-00443" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">1</xref>]. We have selected a number of key examples that are representative of the current literature.
  </p>
 </caption>
